+    `Three-feature subgroup screen over top KIF18A predicates: strongest candidate was ${topTriple.preds.map(predicateText).join(" AND ")} with effect ${fnum(topTriple.subgroup.effect)} (p=${fnum(topTriple.subgroup.p)}, n=${topTriple.subgroup.n1}). The explicit complete subgroup feature_011=\"colorectal\" AND feature_035=1 AND feature_020=0 had effect ${fnum(rComplete.effect)} (p=${fnum(rComplete.p)}, n=${rComplete.n1}).`,
+    topTriple.subgroup.p,
+    topTriple.subgroup.effect,
